Package Catalano.Math

The Catalano.Math namespace contains set of math utilities, which are used by other Catalano framework's namespaces or may be used individually.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RandomNumberGenerator
    Random number generator interface.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Approximation
    Calculate approximations for common math operations.
    ComplexNumber
    Complex Number.
    Constants
    Common mathematical constants.
    Matrix
    Defines a set of methods that works on multidimensional arrays and vectors.
    Matrix3x3
    A class representing 3x3 matrix.
    Random
    This is a high quality random number generator as a replacement of the standard Random class of Java system.
    RationalNumber
    Rational Number.
    SparseArray
    Sparse array of double values.
    Special
    Set of special mathematic functions.
    TaylorSeries
    Compute functions using Taylor series expansion.
    Tools
    Set of mathematical tools.
    UniversalGenerator
    The so called "Universal Generator" based on multiplicative congruential method, which originally appeared in "Toward a Universal Random Number Generator" by Marsaglia, Zaman and Tsang.
    Vector3
    3D Vector class with X, Y and Z coordinates.
    Vector4
    4D Vector class with X, Y, Z and W coordinates.

Package Catalano.Math Description

The Catalano.Math namespace contains set of math utilities, which are used by other Catalano framework's namespaces or may be used individually.
